This paper is primarily focused on image-text matching, which is a task that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method involves reasoning with Graph Convolutional Networks and using gate and memory mechanisms, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper evaluates its method using recall metrics, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR).
